Berlusconi to Name Bank Italy of Governor Tomorrow, Ansa Says

-- B y   A n d r e w   D a v i s
-- 
2011-10-19T10:28:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-19/berlusconi-to-name-bank-italy-of-governor-tomorrow-ansa-says.html
Prime Minister  Silvio Berlusconi 
will nominate a governor for the Bank of  Italy  tomorrow, Ansa
news agency reported, citing the premier.  The new governor will replace  Mario Draghi , who leaves
Italy to head the  European Central Bank  starting on Nov. 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Davis at 
 abdavis@bloomberg.net  